(232, 1, '2019-12-06 14:06:32', '2019-12-06 12:06:32', 'In casinos all over the world, you will be offered chips for various table games; and sometimes, even for slots! So everyone who wants to gamble at a real brick-and-mortar casino needs to read this guide. It’s very important to learn the rules about chips, how they are used, why they are used, and what they represent. It’s vitally important for you to know about this topic. There are multiple reasons for this, but the following ones are crucial:\r\n<ol start=\"1\">\r\n 	<li>\r\n<h3>The General Quality of Your Own Gambling Experience</h3>\r\n</li>\r\n</ol>\r\nNobody wants to sit at a roulette or a poker table and only then realize that they aren’t entirely sure what the different tokens in the casino stand for! So you don’t want to be distracted by your lack of knowledge about gambling during an exciting casino game.\r\n<ol start=\"2\">\r\n 	<li>\r\n<h3>Control Over Your Stakes and No Unpleasant Surprises</h3>\r\n</li>\r\n</ol>\r\nWhen you have a more precise idea of what the different tokens represent, it’ll be easier for you to control and organize your betting strategy.\r\n<ol start=\"3\">\r\n 	<li>\r\n<h3>Avoid Making Unintentional Rule Violations</h3>\r\n</li>\r\n</ol>\r\nMany people are not sure whether they can take their tokens home, or cash them a while later, and so on. Learn about the casino policies so that you can prevent any misunderstandings!\r\n<ol start=\"4\">\r\n 	<li>\r\n<h3>Hosting Home Poker Nights</h3>\r\n</li>\r\n</ol>\r\nWhile you’re learning more about chips, why not try and provide an authentic casino experience for your home poker night guests. Now wouldn’t that be so much fun?\r\n<ol start=\"5\">\r\n 	<li>\r\n<h3>Discovering New Interests</h3>\r\n</li>\r\n</ol>\r\nDid you know that people collect chips? Old and unique chips are popular at various online auctions.\r\n\r\nSo now that we’ve covered the main reasons why you should learn about the subject, let’s jump into lesson one. After