(334, 1, '2019-12-09 20:43:53', '2019-12-09 18:43:53', 'If you’ve ever wanted to play a life-changing game, then maybe progressive slots are for you. I’m going to be brutally honest here — you will never, ever win thousands of bucks playing roulette or blackjack. The payouts are simply not high enough!\r\n\r\nThat is why I, Aussie, will explain what progressive slots are, how they work, and why you should consider playing them.\r\n<h2>What Are They, and How to Win Them?</h2>\r\nMost slots feature a regular jackpot — one which has a fixed reward. Progressive slots, on the other hand, have a jackpot which increases the more coins you put in the machine. A minuscule percentage of each coin is used to increase the overall jackpot. There are three variants of progressive slots.\r\n<ol>\r\n 	<li>\r\n<h3>Standalone Progressives:</h3>\r\n</li>\r\n</ol>\r\nThe oldest one of them all. The jackpot is increased the more coins are spent in one specific machine, thus the name “standalone.” In most cases, the jackpot on these types of pokies stays under $10,000.\r\n<ol start=\"2\">\r\n 	<li>\r\n<h3>Local Progressives:</h3>\r\n</li>\r\n</ol>\r\nThe logical next step in the evolution of progressive slots. They are local because progressive jackpots of the same type of pokie machine are all linked together within the same establishment. The size of the jackpot network can range from a dozen to literally hundreds of machines, depending on the size of the establishments. The jackpots tend to stay under $1 million, and you’ll often find them to be under $100,000.\r\n<ol start=\"3\">\r\n 	<li>\r\n<h3>Wide-Area-Network Progressives:</h3>\r\n</li>\r\n</ol>\r\nThe cutting edge of progressive slot technology and also one of the most played casino games in the world. This impressive technology links the jackpots from all casinos in the same state. This means that the jackpots are incredibly huge, often over $1 million and in rare cases, over $10 million.\r\n<h3>How to Win the Jackpot?</h3>\r\nUnfortunately, there is no strategy or system which can help you here. Basically, your odds are somewhat similar to winning the lottery. However, you do get more chances per hour with a progressive slot than by participating in the lottery.\r\n\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-333\" src=\"http://aussieplay-blog.local/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/gambling-machine-one-armed-bandit-money-las-vegas-Copy-2.jpg\" alt=\"Progressive slots in Casino\" width=\"880\" height=\"423\" />\r\n\r\nA common fallacy about pokies generally, which tends to be exacerbated by the large progressive jackpots, is that after some period of time, the machine is “due” to pay out. It’s not, and in fact, it never is! Your chances of winning the progressive jackpot are astronomically low.\r\n<h3>How to Win the Jackpot Online?</h3>\r\nWith the advent of the internet, progressive slots have been increasing in popularity. The online variant of progressive slots works very much like their land-based brethren. Every bet you make adds a small amount to the overall progressive jackpot for that particular game. Since there are tons and tons of players wagering online, these online jackpots rival the ones from Atlantic City or Vegas.\r\n\r\nSo here’s a list of the largest online jackpots:\r\n\r\n[supsystic-tables id=6]\r\n<h2>Progressive Slots Demand Max Bets</h2>\r\nAn important fact to remember when playing progressive pokies is that you have to place the maximum bet to gain the progressive jackpot. But it is not advisable to play max coins constantly on the vast majority of pokies. However, if you’re playing progressive, I, Aussie, would recommend the exact opposite. You see, if you don’t go max bet on a progressive jackpot and if you somehow end up getting the progressive jackpot, you’ll get a severely reduced payout. If that happens, I don’t know if anyone could handle that level of frustration!\r\n<h2>Summary</h2>\r\nSo there you go — all you should have in mind regarding progressive slots and the mechanics behind them. I, Aussie, hope this little article has helped illuminate your path towards better gaming.\r\n\r\nSo go forward, my friend. Good luck, have fun and always remember to be responsible!', 'Progressive Slots — Miracle Slot Machines', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '310-revision-v1', '', '', '2019-12-09 20:43:53', '2019-12-09 18:43:53', '', 310, 'http://aussieplay-blog.local/bez-kategorii/310-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
