e face cards bring an immediate win</li>\r\n 	<li>You get three cards</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nSo feel free to hit your favorite casino and try this exciting take on this perennial classic, the amazing game of Baccarat!', 'How to Play 3 Card Baccarat', '', 'future', 'open', 'open', '', 'how-to-play-3-card-baccarat', '', '', '2019-12-16 19:10:05', '2019-12-16 17:10:05', '', 0, 'http://aussieplay-blog.local/?p=535', 0, 'post', '', 0),
